
Here’s what to expect in the week ahead.
ECONOMY
Consumer prices for July will be announced on Tuesday, with no significant change from June expected. Data on housing starts in the United States will also be announced on Tuesday. Those numbers are expected to show little change in July from a month earlier, indicating slow progress in residential construction. 
